Welcome to Susquehanna Group Advisors, Inc.



Susquehanna Group Advisors, Inc. is an independent financial advisory and consulting firm located in Harrisburg, Pennsylvania that specializes in providing municipal advisory services to its Pennsylvania client base.  SGA is an SEC and MSRB registered municipal advisor, and is a member of the National Association of Municipal Advisors (NAMA).
We are fully committed to providing the highest level of municipal advisory service to our Pennsylvania client base.  Because we are an independent, non-dealer financial advisor, we are able to provide impartial, objective and superior advice that is in the best financial interests of our municipal clients. 





 















