Susquehanna Financial Advisors LLC is a boutique wealth management firm, offering exceptional personalized service. We take a comprehensive approach to financial planning, using state of the art tools, in order to make sure your investments are tailored to your particular goals, time horizon and risk tolerance. Susquehanna Financial Advisors is an independent, fee based advisory firm. By exclusively serving a limited number of clients, we are able to provide you with a more personalized experience. 








